author: @JoseliJunior
content: What a moment. She reminded us all why she is the Queen of Pop. It was such a cathartic and historic event, people anticipated it so much and she delivered everything and more. I’ve seen performances on that beach but this time people were crying, laughing, holding each other, and plus everything that she represents, it was entertaining, provocative, well thought out, it pissed off the conservatives, she paid homage to Brazil, people from all over the country showed up, they were chanting her songs, dressing up like her, it was Madonna’s carnival, I could go on and on.
